('243fc451-f564-597a-b86d-55452a85f3ce', '82f91108-38f0-4b1a-b73e-fbaacd6dc557', 'SENIOR_HIGH', 'After a long day of studying, ___ often find myself thinking about my future career.', '在漫長的學習日後，我經常發現自己在思考我未來的職業。', 'I', 'You', 'We', 'They', 'I 是第一人稱單數主格代名詞。', 'I 就是「我」。', '2026-07-05 09:58:22', '2026-07-05 09:58:22'),
('246324b2-63c6-54c1-b186-c63555920b1a', '08d7bf36-48f0-4253-a22b-7357bfa6e2a1', 'SENIOR_HIGH', 'A cup ___ hot tea was on the table.', '桌上有一杯熱茶。', 'of', 'in', 'for', 'by', '介係詞，用來表示內容或單位', 'a cup of... 表示「一杯...的...」', '2026-07-05 10:16:03', '2026-07-05 10:16:03'),
('b5ae09fc-84bf-5ae7-b8cf-7eb1b94bdb0a', '825a281c-8ba8-4992-9d3c-d724865fa454', 'JUNIOR_HIGH', '___ cat is very cute.', '那隻貓非常可愛。', 'That', 'Some', 'Each', 'Every', '形容詞，用來修飾名詞，指稱特定的對象。', '指向特定的對象。', '2026-07-05 13:26:49', '2026-07-05 13:26:49'),
('043f4dc9-4ec5-51a7-822a-34e01cd42a0a', 'c8f5ae6e-0be6-420b-a927-4ab8a3519a32', 'SENIOR_HIGH', 'To improve our English proficiency, ___ should engage in more conversations with native speakers.', '為了提高我們的英文能力，我們應該與母語人士進行更多對話。', 'we', 'you', 'he', 'they', '第一人稱複數代名詞，用於句子中擔任主詞的角色。', 'we = 我 + 其他人 → 我們。', '2026-07-06 11:04:30', '2026-07-06 11:04:30'),
('3f3748d7-9966-56c1-a87c-0bce0b029e0e', '4cb49395-91b8-403d-bb41-77e22ac4ae2f', 'JUNIOR_HIGH', 'I ___ go to school tomorrow.', '我明天將要去上學。', 'will', 'must', 'should', 'can', 'will 為單字，無詞根或詞綴。', 'will → 想到未來將會發生的事。', '2026-07-05 13:36:55', '2026-07-05 13:36:55'),
('fd9b16ff-f9cf-591f-a8e7-39c73dcc804a', '6f473860-59ac-4c93-809a-155f5d561a5f', 'JUNIOR_HIGH', 'Would you like to play ___ us after school?', '放學後你想跟我們一起玩嗎？', 'with', 'by', 'from', 'to', '表示「與...在一起」', '與某人在一起玩 → with', '2026-07-05 13:38:52', '2026-07-05 13:38:52');
